{
  "id": "RAW_aaa684f3",
  "title": "重塑对话框，Second Me 正在发起一场 AI 原生的交流革命",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDc2MjQxMg==&mid=2247492902&idx=1&sn=3fbebb5dd945ab3507f39ef9c3f1ad55",
  "date": "2025-12-24 03:28:00",
  "author": "深思圈",
  "siteName": "深思圈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.7092592592592593\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=952e4a34&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FPmez2eeBibTfSfGoGIWwFjib8UZ8Y2OUoXlgO6A1kgHo8DW72JcdHo2g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n       <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">之前跟Tao博合作过很多次，从MindOS到Mebot，听说最近Second Me新版上线了，马上第一时间体验了一下，于是就有了这篇文章</strong>。</p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">最近，OpenAI 有两个动作非常耐人寻味。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">一个是 ChatGPT 的群聊功能终于面向 Plus 用户全量开放了，你可以把 AI 拉进你和朋友、同事的群组里；另一个，是在海外引发热议的 Beta 功能 \"Chat with Apps\"——ChatGPT 可以直接连接 VS Code、Replit 等应用进行操作。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这两个更新释放了一个极其强烈的信号：<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">AI 正在试图打破\"一对一\"的孤岛，开始联机，开始介入我们的\"关系\"与\"生态\"。</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这时候，我关注到了刚刚发布 1.1 版本的<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> Second Me。</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">如果说 ChatGPT 的进群是为了让工作更高效（在群里帮你总结会议纪要、帮你调用app写代码），那么 Second Me 1.1 的野心则在于：<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">它想让 AI 成为你和朋友之间的\"超级连接器\"和\"社交润滑剂\"。</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">其实早在上个月 1.0 版本发布时，我就注意到了这个产品，当时它已经打出了\"AI原生社交网络\"的定位。它致力于为每个人建立自己的\"身份模型\"——不是虚拟的角色，而是对你真实记忆和逻辑的深度还原。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">如果说 1.0 版本是构建了高保真的\"节点\"，并通过\"发现陌生人\"，来拓展新的\"边\"。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">那么刚刚发布的 1.1 版本，则是着重增强了熟人与半熟人网络中既有的\"边\"。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在体验了一段时间后，我发现它不仅仅是一次 App 的更新，它正在验证一种 AI Native 社交的全新雏形。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:28px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">实测：当 AI 开始介入我们的关系</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Second Me 这次重点更新了 AI 社交玩法，体验是很有意思的。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">你可以拉上朋友的 Second Me，用 AI 一起吐槽老板、合拍带有你们特征的卡通表情包，甚至一起来 Rap battle。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae7ba91b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FXYw8FiaZ9XJ53IZLt6qbroUJweibrqQ0kvtia33bW9cdEjNrVZyVcgzKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=617cbc69&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FW7M5kj7UyVBG7ENofbiaqfq86dEGhMTTNUuIYicKTF1ibTia0AsvJYOaRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这听起来像个游戏，但其底层逻辑却很硬核。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd999984&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FibFMXBJzAUsmYQ7XibZkqZ47MoXlBtfvRWu194kozGUXMsvPDqEibGb3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">得益于 Second Me 独创的\"身份模型建模\"，每个人可以发挥无限的创意，你只需要告诉 AI 主题，你和朋友的 Second Me 就会提取你们真实的身份信息和记忆，将你们的故事融入到创作中。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Second Me 创始人 Tao 在演示中，让自己的 AI 替他去向投资人的 AI 做 Pitch。我也试着让我的 second me 去面试候选人，我的 second me 不仅准确调用了我的项目背景，也精准模仿了我的关注点和思维模式。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"1.9064814814814814\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22fda594&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FKa0GBOoGViahLx7fshvJ0GrpCG1ByZXzeA5aZnMcff8U4bvicUdANHbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:28px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">对话框的革命：从\"被动回复\"到\"主动交付\"</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">如果说社交玩法是\"面子\"，那么对\"对话框\"的重塑，则是 Second Me 1.1 的\"里子\"。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">回想一下，从 ICQ 到微信，到 WhatsApp，过去 30 年来，对话框的形态从未改变：你输入，我回复。它是被动的。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">如果你想在微信里玩点什么，你必须跳出当前的对话，去搜索小程序，去点击链接，去其他 app。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Second Me 1.1 试图用 AI 的 Agency（主动性），来让这一交流方式更加丝滑。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在这个版本中，AI 不再是一个等着你输入指令的工具，而是一个\"懂气氛的气氛组\"。它隐身在对话框背后，时刻感知着你们的上下文和情绪温度。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">比如，当群里大家聊得热火朝天，情绪高涨时，AI 会像变魔术一样，把\"AI 合拍\"的相机推到你们面前——\"这么开心的时刻，不留张影吗？\"</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">当朋友间的玩笑开始升级，变成了互怼，AI 会顺势递给你们一支麦克风——\"别吵了，直接来一场 Rap Battle 吧！</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"850\" data-ratio=\"0.28823529411764703\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b25da215&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3Fzqa0BkPv3AVibxxNr3Bg3GLQzHKgD1KHzlyBe1zicBHCWordZKHUQ1wA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"850\" data-ratio=\"0.30823529411764705\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4dd09d40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FppzO1DKo4DRv69J6udXiccicz4iaXgWTXztPichsbsK1tWvQsQbdVYZzmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这种体验是反直觉的，也是奇妙的。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">我们不再只是为了\"传输信息\"而打开对话框，而是为了\"创造经历\"而聚在一起。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:28px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">底层逻辑：从\"社交图谱\"到\"Context 图谱\"</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">如果说 AI 玩法回应的是\"怎么玩\"的问题，那么 Second Me 1.1 更深层的野心，在于重新定义\"连接的本质\"。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在 PC 时代，百度/谷歌做的是信息图谱（网页链接网页）。&nbsp;</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在移动互联网时代，Facebook 和微信做的是社交图谱（Social Graph，人连接人），抖音做的是兴趣图谱（Interest Graph，人连接内容）。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">那么，AI 时代的社交网络，连接介质是什么？</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Second Me 给出的答案是：<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Identity/ Context。</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1. 连接的重构：去标签化的高维匹配&nbsp;</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在 1.1 版本的\"发现\"页中，匹配也进行了升级。你不再是搜\"25岁、爱运动、北京\"，而是可以告诉 AI：\"我想认识一个对 AI coding 非常感兴趣且有 hands-on 经验，底层价值观和我很一致的人。\"</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">系统发起全网搜寻的依据，不是静态的标签，而是每个人 Second Me 背后那个庞大的、动态的分层记忆模型。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"2.1416666666666666\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69f99937&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FWp2p9xWFYiaF96kCrkklTw0aFEVF76PGTXDkKN8VPqYRHEDba45nWLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img class=\"raw-image\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"2.162962962962963\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c57066a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FCpibNcoQfQmxLAKTuYzV9ZJhMdoXrmc3FnsAS0EKSr29UbPqJo9xyibiaBfEWEb59vwX3fS8GwCZNous86LGayFCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这种连接的颗粒度，是上一代社交产品无法达到的。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2. 关系的养成：共同演进&nbsp;</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">更重要的是，这个 Context 是活的。&nbsp;</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">你读过什么书？你曾和朋友讨论过什么深度话题？你此刻的情绪状态如何？ 这些在对话中实时流动的数据喂养着模型，实时回流，让 AI 变得更像你。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">当然，Context 的深度共享往往伴随着隐私的顾虑。这也是 Second Me 1.1 让我觉得成熟的地方——你可以明确地划分记忆的边界：哪些是\"私有\"的（仅自己可见），哪些是\"社交\"的（其他人可见），面对不同的人也可以用自然语言来设置关系形态和话题边界。正是这种严格的边界感，才让我们可以放心地把\"真实的自己\"交给 AI，让\"深度的连接\"成为可能。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:28px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">写在最后</strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Second Me 1.1 并不完美，它还在早期。但它让我兴奋的地方在于，它没有在\"更好的 Tinder\"或\"更像人的 Chatbot\"这些存量赛道里内卷。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">它选择了一条更新、也更难的路，让 AI 帮助人和人建立真实的、深度的链接。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0px 16px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">当你的 AI 开始替你社交，替你维系关系，甚至替你\"活\"在朋友的对话框里时，我们距离那个\"人机共生\"的未来，才算真正迈近了一步。</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Second Me 1.1 版本通过引入 AI 驱动的“身份模型”和“Context 图谱”，重塑了对话框的交互模式，旨在将 AI 转变为社交“润滑剂”和“超级连接器”，引领 AI 原生社交的新范式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Second Me 1.1 版本通过引入 AI 驱动的“身份模型”和“Context 图谱”，重塑了对话框的交互模式，旨在将 AI 转变为社交“润滑剂”和“超级连接器”，引领 AI 原生社交的新范式。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 AI 原生社交应用 Second Me 1.1 版本如何通过 AI 介入社交关系，实现从传统被动回复到主动交付的对话框革命。该版本核心在于构建每个人独特的“身份模型”和基于此的“Context 图谱”，实现了更高维度的社交匹配和关系养成。Second Me 不满足于传统社交应用的“社交图谱”或“兴趣图谱”，而是以 Identity/Context 为连接介质，让 AI 能够感知用户情绪和上下文，主动创造互动体验。文章还强调了其在隐私保护方面的成熟设计，允许用户自定义记忆边界。整体而言，Second Me 正探索一条全新的 AI 原生社交之路，旨在实现更真实、深度的连接，推动人机共生未来的到来。",
